---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us - Down To Earth Technology | Waco, TX">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="relative min-h-[300px] flex items-center justify-center" class="bg-[rgb(49,100,138)]">
		<div class="relative z-10 text-center text-white px-4">
			<h1 class="font-montserrat font-bold uppercase text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl" class="tracking-[-1.875px] leading-none">
				Got Questions?
			</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Section 1: Contact Form -->
	<section class="relative py-20 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-[1080px] mx-auto px-4">
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
				<div class="space-y-6">
					<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-800 text-xl font-cuprum leading-relaxed">
						<p>Thank you for your interest in Down to Earth Technology' IT consulting, computer network support, business surveillance systems, and other IT services. Please use the form below to submit your information if you have questions about our managed IT support, or if you would like to know more about any of our top-of-the-line servers or selection of premiere business monitoring equipment.</p>
						<blockquote class="border-l-4 border-[#e24d3d] pl-4 my-4 text-[#e24d3d] text-xl font-cuprum leading-relaxed">
							Our clients are very important to us. Down to Earth Technology holds your privacy in the highest regard. We never distribute, sell, or make your personal information available to anyone.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					<div class="space-y-4">
						<h2 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-3xl" class="text-[rgb(226,77,61)] tracking-[-1px]">Contact Us</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-800 text-xl font-cuprum leading-relaxed">
							Call <a href="tel:2545234304" class="text-[#e24d3d] hover:underline">(254) 523-4304</a> or submit the form below.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-6">
					<h2 class="font-montserrat font-bold text-3xl" class="text-[rgb(226,77,61)] tracking-[-1px]">Our IT Team Has Answers</h2>
					<div class="space-y-4 text-gray-800 text-xl font-cuprum leading-relaxed">
						<p>Down to Earth Technology has a team of IT experts ready to help you. We are here to answer your questions. Our team is available in the office Monday through Friday from 9am to 4pm. We pledge to respond to IT service requests with action and plan of follow up action within 1 business day. We are available to remotely access your system and provide the IT support necessary quickly and conveniently, so your business operations are never inturrupted.</p>
						<p>You can also reach out to us anytime at any of our social media sites.</p>
						<p>Thank you for choosing Down to Earth Technology. Looking forward to speaking with you soon!</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Section 2: Map -->
	<section class="relative">
		<div class="w-full h-96">
			<iframe
				src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3389.2!2d-97.1467!3d31.5493!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x0!2zMzHCsDMyJzU3LjUiTiA5N8KwMDgnNDguMSJX!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1234567890"
				width="100%"
				height="100%"
				class="border-0"
				allowfullscreen=""
				loading="lazy"
				referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
				title="Down to Earth Technology Location"></iframe>
		</div>
	</section>

	<Footer />
</Layout>
